      • compare

        float compare(String s1,
              String s2,
              Object... args)
        This method builds the Algorithm instance and uses it for the comparison. It is better to use compare(Algorithm, String, String) if you need to perform many comparisons with the same Algorithm
        Parameters:
        s1 - the first String of the comparison
        s2 - the second String of the comparison
        args - a list of elements that you can provide in order to build the Algorithm instance
        Returns:
        the result of the comparison returned by the chosen Algorithm
